{"tid":1452466,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"電影分享 - 賽德克•巴萊","createTime":"2019-08-12T01:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T01:40:41.000Z","uid":222700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"64cd3db6de0a49587ba048f27b9e2ba5b2f02eb6","tid":1452466,"uid":222700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:23:59.000Z","msg":"《賽德克&middot;巴萊》（賽德克語：Seediq Bale）是一部2011年台灣導演魏德聖拍攝的電影長片。改編自邱若龍漫畫《霧社事件》。片名《賽德克&middot;巴萊》意為「真正的人」，在賽德克語，賽德克（Seediq）是人的意思，而巴萊（Bale）是真正的意思。<br />\n<br />\n 本片分為上下兩集：上集以象徵日本的〈太陽旗〉命名，描寫1930年莫那&middot;魯道帶領族人反抗日本長期壓迫原住民而引發的霧社事件；下集命名為《彩虹橋》，刻畫日軍鎮壓，莫那&middot;魯道帶領賽德克族浴血抵抗的過程，並深入刻畫族人從容犧牲後，越過彩虹橋回歸祖靈的故事。 <br />\n<br />\n關鍵詞: 霧社事件"},{"pid":"b2ad66cbf4ed904675322a474be5165d51e52aa9","tid":1452466,"uid":222700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:24:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"590ed9d6b18e3d99b0df28c79ec38bba236b9d98","tid":1452466,"uid":222700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:28:59.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"2aced48d87c6cb874ce5c4e77c9b43caaa627327","tid":1452466,"uid":226975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:30:36.000Z","msg":"閃靈配樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd1883cb51c4c0a319842cb5aa37ae3a4e14640","tid":1452466,"uid":222700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2aced48d87c6cb874ce5c4e77c9b43caaa627327","tid":1452466,"uid":226975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:30:36.000Z","msg":"閃靈配樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime"